==Yang Wood Monkey (甲申)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露}}) as applicable.

==Yang Wood Monkey (甲申)'s Days==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu}} for {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申}} is as follows.

=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申}} is the 7th day (last day) of {{ill|Hanto|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土}} and the 1st day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮}}.

