{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Wood Monkey|kanji=甲申|romaji=kinoe saru|onyomi=kōshin|p=jiǎshēn|w=chia-shen|mi=ʈ͡ʂja̠²¹ ʂən|y=gaap6 san1|j=gaap6 san1|ci=kaːp̚ ʂɐn|mc=kæp ʂin|oc-bs=kaːp ʔʂin}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Wood Monkey also known as 甲申''' (kinoe saru, kouboku no saru, koushin) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 21st combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Kiboku|ja|癸未|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Otyuu|ja|乙酉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Wood|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Monkey|ja|申|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a restraining relationship ({{ill|Mutual Restraint|ja|五行思想#相剋（そうこく）|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (i.e. Metal overcomes Wood).

==Yang Wood Monkey (甲申)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 24 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
