The day of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 7th day (last day) of {{ill|Hanto|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the 1st day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

