==Yang Wood Monkey (甲申)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 0 or 5 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Kou|ja|甲|1=Kinoe (甲)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|乙|1=Kinoto (乙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|July|ja|7月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Beginning of Autumn|ja|立秋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|White Dew|ja|白露|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

