The day of {{ill|Koushin|ja|甲申|1=Yang Wood Monkey|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is the 7th day (last day) of {{ill|Hanto|ja|犯土|lt=Small Earth|lt_ja=小土|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and the 1st day of {{ill|Shihoumoku|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.

